<section class="lab section section--dark" id="lab">
  <div class="wrap">
    <header class="reveal lab-head">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">AI-driven build lab / 04</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">
          <span class="ja">コードで、可能性を試す。</span>
          <span class="en">Test possibility in code.</span>
        </h2>
      </div>
      <p class="section-lede">
        <span class="ja">
          AI、リアルタイム描画、インタラクションを、小さく速く動かして検証する。
          表現のためだけでなく、プロダクトで本当に使える技術へ落とし込みます。
        </span>
        <span class="en">
          Small, working experiments in AI, real-time rendering and interaction.
          Each one tests how an emerging capability can become production-ready product behavior.
        </span>
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="grid">
      <article class="experiment experiment--signal reveal" data-lab-card>
        <div class="meta">
          <span>EXP / 001</span>
          <span>GENERATIVE SYSTEM</span>
        </div>
        <div class="signal" aria-hidden="true">
          {Array.from({ length: 48 }, (_, i) => <i style={`--angle:${i * 7.5}deg;--scale:${(0.26 + i * 0.017).toFixed(3)}`} />)}
          <b>AI</b>
        </div>
        <div class="copy">
          <h3>
            <span class="ja">生成AIインターフェース</span>
            <span class="en">Generative AI interfaces</span>
          </h3>
          <p>
            <span class="ja">モデルの出力を、そのまま見せず、使える操作と一貫した結果へ変換する。</span>
            <span class="en">Turn model output into controlled interactions and dependable results.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="experiment experiment--space reveal" data-lab-card>
        <div class="meta">
          <span>EXP / 002</span>
          <span>SPATIAL INTERFACE</span>
        </div>
        <div class="space" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="orb orb--one"></div>
          <div class="orb orb--two"></div>
          <div class="orb orb--three"></div>
          <div class="plane"><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i></div>
          <span>XYZ / LIVE</span>
        </div>
        <div class="copy">
          <h3>
            <span class="ja">空間データインターフェース</span>
            <span class="en">Spatial data interfaces</span>
          </h3>
          <p>
            <span class="ja">複雑なデータを、リアルタイム描画と操作で素早く把握できる状態へ。</span>
            <span class="en">Make complex data legible through real-time rendering and direct manipulation.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="experiment experiment--type reveal" data-lab-card>
        <div class="meta">
          <span>EXP / 003</span>
          <span>PRODUCT FEEDBACK</span>
        </div>
        <div class="feedback" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="feedback-line">
            <span class="feedback-progress"></span>
            <span class="feedback-pulse"></span>
          </div>
          <ol>
            <li>
              <i>01</i>
              <b>INPUT</b>
              <span>Signal captured</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <i>02</i>
              <b>BUILD</b>
              <span>Change running</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <i>03</i>
              <b>LEARN</b>
              <span>Next action</span>
            </li>
          </ol>
          <div class="feedback-result">
            <span class="feedback-check">✓</span>
            <p><b>UPDATE LIVE</b><small>Feedback became behavior</small></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="copy">
          <h3>
            <span class="ja">動きで伝わるフィードバック</span>
            <span class="en">Feedback that communicates</span>
          </h3>
          <p>
            <span class="ja">入力、処理、結果をひと続きに。説明を増やさず、いま何が起きたかを伝える。</span>
            <span class="en">Connect input, processing and outcome so every change feels immediate and clear.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  if (matchMedia("(hover: hover) and (pointer: fine)").matches) {
    document.querySelectorAll<HTMLElement>("[data-lab-card]").forEach((card) => {
      card.addEventListener("pointermove", (event) => {
        const rect = card.getBoundingClientRect();
        card.style.setProperty("--mx", `${((event.clientX - rect.left) / rect.width) * 100}%`);
        card.style.setProperty("--my", `${((event.clientY - rect.top) / rect.height) * 100}%`);
      }, { passive: true });
    });
  }
</script>

<style>
  .lab {
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #0c0b0a;
  }

  .lab-head {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
    align-items: end;
    gap: 48px;
  }

  .lab-head .section-lede { margin: 0; }

  .grid {
    margin-top: clamp(52px, 7vw, 92px);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.28fr 0.72fr;
    grid-template-rows: repeat(2, minmax(330px, 42vw));
    max-height: 1180px;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .experiment {
    --mx: 50%;
    --my: 50%;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    min-height: 330px;
    padding: 22px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(243, 240, 235, 0.12);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    background:
      radial-gradient(500px circle at var(--mx) var(--my), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.075), transparent 42%),
      #141210;
    isolation: isolate;
  }

  .experiment::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: -1;
    opacity: 0.4;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.035) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,.035) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 38px 38px;
    mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, #000, transparent 78%);
  }

  .experiment--signal { grid-row: span 2; }

  .meta {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 5;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 16px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: .13em;
    color: rgba(243, 240, 235, 0.42);
  }

  .copy {
    position: absolute;
    z-index: 5;
    left: 22px;
    right: 22px;
    bottom: 22px;
    padding-top: 80px;
    background: linear-gradient(transparent, rgba(12, 11, 10, 0.92) 68%);
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: clamp(24px, 3.1vw, 48px);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.02;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-display);
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .copy p {
    margin-top: 10px;
    max-width: 46ch;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--text-on-dark-muted);
  }

  .signal {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 70px 30px 150px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    transform-style: preserve-3d;
    perspective: 900px;
  }

  .signal i {
    position: absolute;
    width: clamp(130px, 19vw, 280px);
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    border: 1px solid rgba(240, 131, 79, 0.28);
    border-radius: 44% 56% 62% 38% / 55% 40% 60% 45%;
    transform: rotate(var(--angle)) scale(var(--scale));
    animation: signal-spin 15s linear infinite;
  }

  .signal b {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    font-size: clamp(70px, 14vw, 210px);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -.09em;
    color: transparent;
    -webkit-text-stroke: 1px rgba(255, 164, 106, 0.9);
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 30px rgba(236, 80, 20, .2));
  }

  @keyframes signal-spin {
    to { rotate: 360deg; }
  }

  .space {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 52px 22px 122px;
    perspective: 700px;
    transform-style: preserve-3d;
  }

  .plane {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 13% 8%;
    border: 1px solid rgba(243, 240, 235, .14);
    transform: rotateX(64deg) rotateZ(-18deg);
    background:
      linear-gradient(rgba(243,240,235,.08) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(243,240,235,.08) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 34px 34px;
    animation: plane-drift 8s var(--ease-in-out) infinite;
  }

  .plane i {
    position: absolute;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #ff7441;
    box-shadow: 0 0 14px #ff7441;
  }
  .plane i:nth-child(1) { left: 14%; top: 24%; }
  .plane i:nth-child(2) { left: 70%; top: 18%; }
  .plane i:nth-child(3) { left: 54%; top: 72%; }
  .plane i:nth-child(4) { left: 28%; top: 62%; }

  @keyframes plane-drift {
    50% { transform: rotateX(59deg) rotateZ(-13deg) translate3d(0, -8px, 22px); }
  }

  .orb {
    position: absolute;
    z-index: 3;
    width: 68px;
    height: 68px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 35% 30%, #ffc7a6, #ff5926 35%, #4912b8 72%, #090807);
    box-shadow: 0 18px 42px rgba(255, 75, 24, .24);
    animation: orbit-float 5s var(--ease-in-out) infinite;
  }
  .orb--one { left: 22%; top: 18%; }
  .orb--two { right: 18%; top: 46%; width: 38px; height: 38px; animation-delay: -1.7s; }
  .orb--three { left: 46%; bottom: 5%; width: 22px; height: 22px; animation-delay: -3.4s; }

  @keyframes orbit-float {
    50% { transform: translate3d(8px, -15px, 30px); }
  }

  .space > span {
    position: absolute;
    right: 2px;
    top: 2px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 8px;
    letter-spacing: .12em;
    color: rgba(243,240,235,.4);
  }

  .feedback {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 62px 22px 132px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .feedback-line {
    position: absolute;
    left: 9%;
    right: 9%;
    top: 50%;
    height: 1px;
    background: rgba(243, 240, 235, .14);
  }

  .feedback-progress {
    position: absolute;
    inset: -1px auto -1px 0;
    width: 34%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #8072ed, #ff8d6a);
    transform-origin: left;
    animation: feedback-progress 4.8s var(--ease-in-out) infinite;
  }

  .feedback-pulse {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 0;
    width: 11px;
    height: 11px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    translate: -50% -50%;
    background: #ff9a73;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 7px rgba(255, 137, 97, .09), 0 0 25px rgba(255, 116, 70, .55);
    animation: feedback-pulse 4.8s var(--ease-in-out) infinite;
  }

  .feedback ol {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .feedback li {
    min-width: 0;
    padding: 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(243, 240, 235, .13);
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: rgba(20, 18, 16, .88);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    animation: feedback-card 4.8s var(--ease-in-out) infinite;
  }

  .feedback li:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: -3.2s; }
  .feedback li:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: -1.6s; }

  .feedback li i,
  .feedback li b,
  .feedback li span {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-style: normal;
  }

  .feedback li i {
    color: #ff8b62;
    font-size: 8px;
    letter-spacing: .1em;
  }

  .feedback li b {
    margin-top: 16px;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: .08em;
  }

  .feedback li span {
    margin-top: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
    color: rgba(243, 240, 235, .42);
    font-size: 7px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
  }

  .feedback-result {
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    bottom: -5px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 9px 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(138, 223, 179, .24);
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(30, 55, 42, .45);
    opacity: .35;
    transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(5px);
    animation: feedback-result 4.8s var(--ease-in-out) infinite;
  }

  .feedback-check {
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #9be0b7;
    color: #142219;
    font-size: 11px;
  }

  .feedback-result p,
  .feedback-result b,
  .feedback-result small {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .feedback-result b { font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: .1em; }
  .feedback-result small { margin-top: 2px; color: rgba(243,240,235,.48); font-size: 7px; white-space: nowrap; }

  @keyframes feedback-progress {
    0%, 9% { transform: scaleX(.03); opacity: .25; }
    70%, 88% { transform: scaleX(2.92); opacity: 1; }
    100% { transform: scaleX(2.92); opacity: .2; }
  }

  @keyframes feedback-pulse {
    0%, 9% { left: 0; }
    70%, 100% { left: 100%; }
  }

  @keyframes feedback-card {
    0%, 28%, 100% { border-color: rgba(243,240,235,.13); transform: translateY(0); }
    13% { border-color: rgba(255,143,101,.62); transform: translateY(-4px); }
  }

  @keyframes feedback-result {
    0%, 64%, 100% { opacity: .3; transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(5px); }
    76%, 90% { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 920px) {
    .lab-head { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 22px; }
    .lab-head .section-lede { margin-top: 0; }
    .grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      grid-template-rows: 600px 410px 410px;
      max-height: none;
    }
    .experiment--signal { grid-row: auto; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .grid { grid-template-rows: 520px 360px 360px; }
    .experiment { padding: 18px; }
    .copy { left: 18px; right: 18px; bottom: 18px; }
    .signal { inset: 62px 14px 130px; }
    .space { inset: 50px 14px 110px; }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .signal i, .plane, .orb,
    .feedback-progress, .feedback-pulse, .feedback li, .feedback-result {
      animation: none;
    }
  }
</style>
